<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>代理 on 路飞博客</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86/</link><description>Recent content in 代理 on 路飞博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2023 21:35:50 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Rclone Browser代理设置</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/rclone-browser%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2023 21:35:50 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/rclone-browser%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/10/7913e2072e602cf40fe4c04867184b64.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Rclone Browser代理设置" />&lt;p>假设你已经安装了&lt;code>rclone&lt;/code>,并配置好了各大网盘&lt;/p>
&lt;p>那么在&lt;code>Rclone Browser&lt;/code>查看谷歌硬盘内容,是看不了的,但是如果你已经开启了&lt;code>科学上网&lt;/code>,则按照下面的方法&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">socks5://127.0.0.1:10808
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;code>10808&lt;/code>端口是v2ray的代理端口&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如果是小狐狸则是 &lt;code>7890&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">socks5://127.0.0.1:7890
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/09/a7a2b0af127a3a1e82a8b4ea2bf67582.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="Pasted image 20230914213555"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>下载的时候要加上参数,避免有些文件被误认为病毒无法下载:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">--drive-acknowledge-abuse
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/09/3f3048d9fc55b43d561e0eeef6a12186.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="Pasted image 20230914221303"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>cmd终端开启代理:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>小狐狸:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">http_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>socks5://127.0.0.1:7890
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">https_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>socks5://127.0.0.1:7890
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>v2ray:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">http_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>socks5://127.0.0.1:10808
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">https_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>socks5://127.0.0.1:10808
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>取消代理:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">http_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">https_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>